Description :
        Princess-nim, Please Take My Misfortune Away!,     ! atmanhwawebsiteWhenever Sa Junmok goes on a picnic, the bus always breaks down. When he travels, the hotel always has a blackout. Even when he eats group meals, he's the only one who gets food poisoning. As an unlucky omega, this is Junmok's everyday life. Despite his bad luck, he decided to experience all the things he missed out on once he entered college, including having a passionate romance with a handsome and charming alpha!However, his inherent bad luck didn't improve just because he got into a prestigious university. Things get even more complicated when he gets involved with the campus celebrity, Gong Jurim, who seems to make everything worse. Although Gong Jurim is the perfect alpha who embodies Junmok's ideal type, every time they meet, it ends in disaster. Junmok resolves to avoid him at all costs."I know I've done a lot wrong, but let's stop seeing each other because I'm bad luck.""Why, because you feel guilty for causing trouble?""That's part of it, but Gongju sunbaenim, you're bad for my heart."However, after a night of drinking, Junmok wakes up to find himself in bed with Gong Jurim, who is inexplicably naked."You said I was your type. My face, my body, even my voice.""Gongju-nim?""You have to take responsibility for your confession."Can the unlucky Junmok find happiness in a relationship with the infamous Gong Jurim? Princess, please take away my misfortune!Maybe you like !
